    "description": "Mapping of Non-opt-in Entities (NOIEs) to substations and electrical buses in ERCOT.\n\nA NOIE is the default provider in its territory, which is not paticipating in the competitive retail market, and:\n\n> at its sole discretion may authorize third party QSEs to provide Load Resource and ERS services within their service territory. "
